notam.notam_html:
CLOSURE OF TAXIWAY P2 BETWEEN AIRCRAFT STANDS E24 AND E30 FOR
PARTIAL
PAVEMENT REHABILITATION.
- ACCESSIBILITY:
. P2 ACCESSIBLE ONLY TO AIRCRAFT BOUND FOR STANDS E14, E16, E18,
E20, E22, E32, E34.
. STAND E08 IS CLOSED AND SERVES AS A TURNAROUND SLIDER FOR PUSHBACK
PROCEDURES FROM STANDS E18, E20, AND E22.
. STANDS E24, E26, AND E30 ARE CLOSED
. STANDS E32 AND E34 ARE LIMITED TO CODE C AIRCRAFT
- DEPARTURE PROCEDURES:
1) PUSHBACKS:
. E14: PUSHBACK FACING WEST AND AIRCRAFT EXITING WITH ENGINES VIA
TE1 . E16: PUSHBACK FACING WEST AND AIRCRAFT EXITING WITH ENGINES
VIA TE1 . E18: LONG PUSHBACK FACING EAST AND TURNAROUND FACING SOUTH
ON E08 . E20: LONG PUSHBACK FACING EAST AND TURNAROUND FACING SOUTH
ON E08 . E22: LONG PUSHBACK FACING EAST AND TURNAROUND FACING SOUTH
ON E08 . E32: PUSHBACK FACING EAST ACCORDING TO THE SPECIFIC
PROCEDURE
. E34: PUSHBACK FACING EAST ACCORDING TO THE SPECIFIC PROCEDURE 2)
AIRCRAFT ENGINE EXIT:
. THE EXIT OF THE AIRCRAFT WITH ENGINE VIA TE1 IS PROHIBITED FOR ANY
TYPE OF AIRCRAFT, EXCEPT AFTER PUSHING BACK INTO THE DRAWER CREATED
AT STAND E08 FOR AIRCRAFT DEPARTING FROM STANDS E18, E20, AND E22,
OR FOR AIRCRAFT DEPARTING FROM STANDS E14 AND E16
. THE EXIT OF THE AIRCRAFT VIA TE2 IS PROHIBITED FOR CODE D AND E
AIRCRAFT

ALDERGROVE, BELFAST CITY, EDINBURGH, GLASGOW, INVERNESS, NEWCASTLE,
PRESTWICK AND SUMBURGH.
COMBINING THE K AND N SERIES - THE K SERIES WILL BE REMOVED AND BE

AND COVERED BY THE D SERIES.

AND COVERED BY THE U SERIES.
CHANGE OF SERIES FOR NOTAM THAT HAVE AN AD IN FIELD A - ALL NAV 
WARNINGS WITH AN AD IN FIELD A WILL BE ISSUED UNDER THAT AD SERIES.
ALL NAV AIDS WITH AN AD IN FIELD A WILL BE ISSUED UNDER THAT AD 
SERIES.
AIRSPACE NOTAM WITH AN AD IN FIELD A WILL BE ISSUED UNDER THAT AD 
SERIES. WITH THE EXCEPTION OF UNLICENSED AD (E SERIES) AND THOSE 
CATERED FOR IN THE J SERIES.
NOTAM WITH A START DATE AFTER 02 OCT WILL BE ISSUED IN THEIR NEW
